  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Rain Hat/DST</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/32px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/32px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p>The <b>Rain Hat</b> is a craftable <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dress\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dress\">Dress</a> item from the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Reign of Giants\">Reign of Giants</a></i> DLC. It requires 2 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moleworm\" title=\"Moleworm\">Moleworms</a>, 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Straw_Hat\" title=\"Straw Hat\">Straw Hat</a>, and 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bone_Shards\" title=\"Bone Shards\">Bone Shard</a> to craft and an <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Alchemy_Engine\" title=\"Alchemy Engine\">Alchemy Engine</a> to prototype. The <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sewing_Kit\" title=\"Sewing Kit\">Sewing Kit</a> repairs 50% of its durability.\n</p><p>When worn during <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rain\" title=\"Rain\">Rain</a>, it protects against <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wetness\" title=\"Wetness\">Wetness</a> gain by 70%. Additionally, it insulates the player against <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lightning\" title=\"Lightning\">Lightning</a> strikes and the electric shocks of a charged <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Volt_Goat\" title=\"Volt Goat\">Volt Goat</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rain_Hat/DST#Skins\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Skins</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rain_Hat/DST#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rain_Hat/DST#Assets\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Assets</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rain_Hat/DST#Gallery\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gallery</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Skins\"><img alt=\"Voidbag Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Voidbag_Icon.png/32px-Voidbag_Icon.png?3b640b\" width=\"32\" height=\"33\"> Skins</span></h2>\n<p><span class=\"box headnote\"><i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Glommer%27s_Flower.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Glommer&#x27;s Flower.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Glommer%27s_Flower.png/25px-Glommer%27s_Flower.png?22167d\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\"></a> Main article:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Belongings#Head_items\" title=\"Belongings\">Belongings</a></span><br>\n</p>\n<div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Cowboy_Straw_Hat_-_Rain_Hat_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cowboy Straw Hat - Rain Hat Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cowboy_Straw_Hat_-_Rain_Hat_Icon.png/120px-Cowboy_Straw_Hat_-_Rain_Hat_Icon.png?368e41\" width=\"120\" height=\"108\"></a></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Cowboy Rain Hat</b></div><div><br>(associated with: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Cowboy_Straw_Hat_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cowboy Straw Hat Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cowboy_Straw_Hat_Icon.png/32px-Cowboy_Straw_Hat_Icon.png?aecd79\" width=\"32\" height=\"23\"></a>)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Bonnet_-_Rain_Hat_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rain Bonnet - Rain Hat Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Bonnet_-_Rain_Hat_Icon.png/120px-Rain_Bonnet_-_Rain_Hat_Icon.png?58cb89\" width=\"120\" height=\"87\"></a></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Rain Bonnet</b></div><div class=\"skin-description\"><i>A dear little bonnet to keep your head dry.</i></div><div><br>(associated with: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Straw_Bonnet_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Straw Bonnet Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Straw_Bonnet_Icon.png/32px-Straw_Bonnet_Icon.png?3a0138\" width=\"32\" height=\"23\"></a>)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Floppy_Straw_Hat_-_Rain_Hat_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Floppy Straw Hat - Rain Hat Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Floppy_Straw_Hat_-_Rain_Hat_Icon.png/120px-Floppy_Straw_Hat_-_Rain_Hat_Icon.png?b35572\" width=\"120\" height=\"101\"></a></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Floppy Rain Hat</b></div><div><br>(associated with: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Floppy_Straw_Hat_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Floppy Straw Hat Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Floppy_Straw_Hat_Icon.png/32px-Floppy_Straw_Hat_Icon.png?b10388\" width=\"32\" height=\"31\"></a>)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Looks_Like_Rain_Hat_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Looks Like Rain Hat Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Looks_Like_Rain_Hat_Icon.png/120px-Looks_Like_Rain_Hat_Icon.png?19782f\" width=\"120\" height=\"99\"></a></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Looks Like Rain Hat</b></div><div class=\"skin-description\"><i>Keep your noggin dry!</i></div><div><br>(associated with: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rancher_Straw_Hat_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rancher Straw Hat Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rancher_Straw_Hat_Icon.png/32px-Rancher_Straw_Hat_Icon.png?ca468f\" width=\"32\" height=\"22\"></a>)</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Rain Hats require <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moleworm\" title=\"Moleworm\">Moleworms</a> to craft because the moleskin is known for its water-resistance.</li>\n<li>The crafting recipe used to require <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tentacle_Spot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tentacle Spot\">Tentacle Spots</a> instead of Moleworms.</li>\n<li>Wearing this hat while standing under <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tree\" title=\"Tree\">Tree</a> provides sufficient Wetness protection from rain.</li></ul>\n<div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Assets\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Research_Notes\" title=\"Research Notes\"><img alt=\"Research Notes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Research_Notes.png/32px-Research_Notes.png?ef2da4\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Assets</span></h2>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Rain_Hat-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rain_Hat/DST#Rain_Hat-0\">Rain Hat</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Cowboy_Rain_Hat-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rain_Hat/DST#Cowboy_Rain_Hat-0\">Cowboy Rain Hat</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Rain_Bonnet-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rain_Hat/DST#Rain_Bonnet-0\">Rain Bonnet</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Floppy_Rain_Hat-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rain_Hat/DST#Floppy_Rain_Hat-0\">Floppy Rain Hat</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Looks_Like_Rain_Hat-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rain_Hat/DST#Looks_Like_Rain_Hat-0\">Looks Like Rain Hat</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Hat_Dropped.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Dropped\"><img alt=\"Dropped\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Hat_Dropped.png/120px-Rain_Hat_Dropped.png?f949b5\" width=\"120\" height=\"91\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Dropped</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Hat_Equipped.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Equipped\"><img alt=\"Equipped\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Hat_Equipped.png/120px-Rain_Hat_Equipped.png?12981a\" width=\"120\" height=\"32\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"> Equipped</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Cowboy_Rain_Hat_Dropped.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Dropped\"><img alt=\"Dropped\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cowboy_Rain_Hat_Dropped.png/120px-Cowboy_Rain_Hat_Dropped.png?afed7e\" width=\"120\" height=\"72\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Dropped</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Cowboy_Rain_Hat_Equipped.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Equipped\"><img alt=\"Equipped\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cowboy_Rain_Hat_Equipped.png/120px-Cowboy_Rain_Hat_Equipped.png?f73b1b\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"> Equipped</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Bonnet_Dropped.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Dropped\"><img alt=\"Dropped\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Bonnet_Dropped.png/120px-Rain_Bonnet_Dropped.png?d58a7a\" width=\"120\" height=\"84\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Dropped</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Bonnet_Equipped.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Equipped\"><img alt=\"Equipped\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Bonnet_Equipped.png/120px-Rain_Bonnet_Equipped.png?d15728\" width=\"120\" height=\"31\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"> Equipped</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Floppy_Rain_Hat_Dropped.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Dropped\"><img alt=\"Dropped\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Floppy_Rain_Hat_Dropped.png/120px-Floppy_Rain_Hat_Dropped.png?713a8d\" width=\"120\" height=\"68\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Dropped</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Floppy_Rain_Hat_Equipped.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Equipped\"><img alt=\"Equipped\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Floppy_Rain_Hat_Equipped.png/120px-Floppy_Rain_Hat_Equipped.png?679f6a\" width=\"120\" height=\"27\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"> Equipped</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Looks_Like_Rain_Hat_Dropped.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Dropped\"><img alt=\"Dropped\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Looks_Like_Rain_Hat_Dropped.png/120px-Looks_Like_Rain_Hat_Dropped.png?7749b7\" width=\"120\" height=\"58\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Dropped</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Looks_Like_Rain_Hat_Equipped.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Equipped\"><img alt=\"Equipped\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Looks_Like_Rain_Hat_Equipped.png/120px-Looks_Like_Rain_Hat_Equipped.png?78ca4e\" width=\"120\" height=\"20\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"> Equipped</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:DST_Hook_Line_and_Inker_Trailer_Wilson.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The Rain Hat as seen in the Hook, Line, and Inker trailer.\"><img alt=\"The Rain Hat as seen in the Hook, Line, and Inker trailer.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/DST_Hook_Line_and_Inker_Trailer_Wilson.png/120px-DST_Hook_Line_and_Inker_Trailer_Wilson.png?cbc7f0\" width=\"120\" height=\"68\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">The Rain Hat as seen in the <i>Hook, Line, and Inker</i> trailer.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Spring_RoG_poster.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Wilson with a Rain Hat in Reign of Giants spring promo poster\"><img alt=\"Wilson with a Rain Hat in Reign of Giants spring promo poster\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Spring_RoG_poster.png/120px-Spring_RoG_poster.png?fdc79c\" width=\"120\" height=\"68\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Wilson with a Rain Hat in Reign of Giants spring promo poster</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Hat_Wilson.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Wilson wearing a Rain Hat.\"><img alt=\"Wilson wearing a Rain Hat.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Hat_Wilson.png/120px-Rain_Hat_Wilson.png?41b16e\" width=\"120\" height=\"43\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wilson\" title=\"Wilson\">Wilson</a> wearing a Rain Hat.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Hat_Willow.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Willow wearing a Rain Hat.\"><img alt=\"Willow wearing a Rain Hat.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Hat_Willow.png/120px-Rain_Hat_Willow.png?33e777\" width=\"120\" height=\"43\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Willow\" title=\"Willow\">Willow</a> wearing a Rain Hat.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Hat_Wolfgang.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Wolfgang wearing a Rain Hat.\"><img alt=\"Wolfgang wearing a Rain Hat.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Hat_Wolfgang.png/111px-Rain_Hat_Wolfgang.png?522dbe\" width=\"111\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wolfgang\" title=\"Wolfgang\">Wolfgang</a> wearing a Rain Hat.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Hat_Wendy.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Wendy wearing a Rain Hat.\"><img alt=\"Wendy wearing a Rain Hat.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Hat_Wendy.png/120px-Rain_Hat_Wendy.png?8609b7\" width=\"120\" height=\"43\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wendy\" title=\"Wendy\">Wendy</a> wearing a Rain Hat.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Hat_WX-78.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"WX-78 wearing a Rain Hat.\"><img alt=\"WX-78 wearing a Rain Hat.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Hat_WX-78.png/120px-Rain_Hat_WX-78.png?7ad00b\" width=\"120\" height=\"43\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/WX-78\" title=\"WX-78\">WX-78</a> wearing a Rain Hat.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Hat_Wickerbottom.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Wickerbottom wearing a Rain Hat.\"><img alt=\"Wickerbottom wearing a Rain Hat.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Hat_Wickerbottom.png/120px-Rain_Hat_Wickerbottom.png?5a103e\" width=\"120\" height=\"43\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wickerbottom\" title=\"Wickerbottom\">Wickerbottom</a> wearing a Rain Hat.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Hat_Woodie.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Woodie wearing a Rain Hat.\"><img alt=\"Woodie wearing a Rain Hat.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Hat_Woodie.png/120px-Rain_Hat_Woodie.png?fc5b0c\" width=\"120\" height=\"43\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Woodie\" title=\"Woodie\">Woodie</a> wearing a Rain Hat.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Hat_Wes.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Wes wearing a Rain Hat.\"><img alt=\"Wes wearing a Rain Hat.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_Hat_Wes.png/120px-Rain_Hat_Wes.png?542ec5\" width=\"120\" height=\"43\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wes\" title=\"Wes\">Wes</a> wearing a Rain Hat.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rain_Hat_Maxwell.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Maxwell wearing a Rain Hat.\"><img alt=\"Maxwell wearing a Rain Hat.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rain_H